STM32CubeF0 Firmware Package
============================
This directory contians parts of STM32CubeF0 1.7.0, which are
relevant to the NUCLEO-F091 board. To preserve compatibilty
with STM32CubeF0, this directory preserves the sub-directory
structure of STM32CubeF0, so the relative paths should work for
the full version of STM32CubeF0 as well.
